  "text": "Mean time interval required for complete bone union ranged from 3.5 -10.3 months for EF and 5.2 -9.8 months for IMN. This was reported to be 5.6 months for dual plating [CITATION_1] and 6.1 months for cannulated screws [CITATION_2] .",
